            "title": "黑期高水近百點 重磅港股ADR普遍升 阿里逼近百元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時11分升79點或0.38%，報20881點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報20862點，較香港上日現貨收市高72點或0.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣424元，較上日香港收市高3.2元或0.76%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣99.6元，較上日香港收市高1.98元或2.02%</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20231207_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20231207_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣151.2元，較上日香港收市高0.38元或0.26%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣160.3元，較上日香港收市低1.84元或1.14%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣40元，較上日香港收市高0.41元或1.04%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">匯控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣80.9元，較上日香港收市高0.81元或1.01%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣54.3元，較上日香港收市高0.24元或0.45%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣313元，較上日香港收市高1.04元或0.33%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣44.2元，較上日香港收市高0.23元或0.52%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣6.4元，較上日香港收市低0.02元或0.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報20971點，升131點，較上日恒指收市20789點，高水181點。科指期貨夜市收報5031點，較上日科指收市高水54點；國指期貨夜市收報7713點，較上日國指收市高水69點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14683098-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e8%bf%91%e7%99%be%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e6%99%ae%e9%81%8d%e5%8d%87-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e9%80%bc%e8%bf%91%e7%99%be%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
